Ferrari car prices in India: The price of Ferrari cars in India starts from ₹ 3.76 Cr for the Roma while the most expensive Ferrari car in India one is the SF90 Stradale with a price of ₹ 7.50 Cr. The newest model in the Ferrari line-up is the 296 GTB with a price tag of ₹ 5.40 Cr
The Italian brand has now announced prices for the Purosangue in India. According to a report by Autocar India, Ferrari has priced the Purosangue at a whopping Rs 10.50 crore (ex-showroom).
